:

1. *Sred* njega su se okupili ljudi sa različitim ukusima. (In the midst of him, people with different tastes gathered.) 
2. Kao deca smo se igrali u *sred* ulice. (As children, we played in the middle of the street.)
3. Imali smo nezgodan susret u *sred* noći. (We had an unpleasant encounter in the middle of the night.) 
4. On je ušao u sobu u *sred* našeg razgovora. (He entered the room in the middle of our conversation.) 
5. Čula sam zvuk iz *sred* šume. (I heard a sound from the middle of the forest.)